{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d6e41f2aee","title":"上海音乐学院贺晓秋遗书（摘录）","origin":"史中兴著《贺绿汀传》，上海音乐出版社2000年5月第一版。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7273760fe8","index":0,"year":1968,"month":4,"day":6,"articleId":"d6e41f2aee"}],"tags":[{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"58c996b27d","name":"贺晓秋"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a0b0579225","type":"title","text":"上海音乐学院贺晓秋遗书（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee"},{"id":"e283085990","type":"authors","text":"贺晓秋","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee"},{"id":"47c9c9cb9d","type":"subtitle","text":"〖贺晓秋，女，上海音乐学院理论作曲系学生，上海音乐学院院长贺绿汀的二女儿。因不堪父母被打成“叛徒”，全家遭到迫害，在家开煤气自杀。〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee"},{"id":"0491bde318","type":"appellation","text":"姐姐、姐夫：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee"},{"id":"3b00c8d655","type":"paragraph","text":"这是我最后一次叫你们了。以后怎么样我不知道，也不想知道。我对生活一点都不感兴趣，我对今后也不抱任何幻想。我的面前只是一片黑暗。我已看到了自己前途的尽头。我现在已无法摆脱这个邪魔纠缠。我现在担心的只是你们。不要因为我的不幸而给你们今后带来什么麻烦……","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee"},{"id":"53f16412c3","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee"},{"id":"eb30ead6e3","type":"paragraph","text":" 晓秋68.4.6","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee"}],"page":{"id":"b0ea7c8d5f","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"d6e41f2aee","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}